addWaypoint 
Behavior: global 
Game: Armed Assault (1.00) 
Description: Adds (or inserts when index is given) a new waypoint to a group. 
The waypoint is placed randomly within a circle with the given center 
 and radius. 
The function returns a waypoint with format [group, index].    
Syntax:  
 Array = groupName addWaypoint [center, radius] or [center, radius, index] 
Parameters: 
groupName: Group 
[center, radius]: Array 
center: Position or Object 
index: Number 
Return Value: 
 Array - format Waypoint